Install dnslib

pip3 install dnslib


Run 

sudo python3 get_dns.py


Open another terminal, Run dig

dig @1.1.1.1 cricbuzz.com


Expected response: 

[Query] Process=dig src=9.109.124.153 dst=1.1.1.1 S_port=43461 D_port=53 Name=cricbuzz.com. Query_type=A
<__main__.c_ubyte_Array_96 object at 0x7f71ab112740>

=========================
^lEQ/@  m|5=Vn$cricbuzzcom)

>~(Z
=========================
[Response] Process=dig src=1.1.1.1 dst=9.109.124.153 S_port=53 D_port=43461 Name=cricbuzz.com. Query_type=A Query_data=35.200.167.142
<__main__.c_ubyte_Array_104 object at 0x7f71ab112740>

=========================
lq8EhU9@3       m|5Ancricbuzzcom
                                m#È§)
